<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka ngaina e Lalgam lopi,
 Siemthak leia hung lang ding chu,
 Kumsang vaihawm ding nilopi,
 Lenkawl chu tun hung engin.

[V2]
 Gam lopi ka kumsawt gam,
 A ngaiin ka lieng taluoi;
 Gam lopi ka kumsawt gam,
 A ngaiin ka lieng taluoi.

[V3]
 2. A cham sawt ngei ka Lal gamtiem,
 Gam luoh thu la ding thangvan ah,
 Ngaiin zaila'n pak bang chawi ka,
 Lei Zion a ngui zo tai.

[V4]
 3. Sietlei lalte kawmah Lalpa,
 Ka lungkhamna ka genthei puoi;
 Mi chengcheng te kawmah Lalpa,
 Ka hun ngaih ka gen thei puoi.

[V5]
 4. Ka hun ngai ie ka Lal nunnem,
 Na thawkna ngilhni nei puong ie,
 Na lautha'n hinna lenkawl eng,
 Nuomah nau bang ei pui in.</lyrics>
<title>Lalgam Lopi</title>
<author>C.Z. Huala</author>
<hymn_number>235</hymn_number>
</song>